dct_description_sm: Aut: il P. Cosmografo Coronelli ; All Illustriss: S. Franc: Gafparoli, Nobile Fanese.
California shown as an unlabeled island with a large, indented northern coast.
Includes a dedicatory panel and a coat-of-arms.
